GET /messages/[type]/[region]/[realm]/[name]/[creatorId]

POST /messages
    type
    region
    realm
    name
    creatorID
    text

    ON POST --> SEND new message to creatorID  && GET ALL ID FOR type region realm name and SEND message

GET /messages
GET ALL GUILDS for user --> GET ALL MESSAGE ROOM WITH ALL GUILD
GET ALL MESSAGE ROOM with creatorID == userId
GET ALL CHARACTER for user --> GET ALL MESSAGE ROOM WITH ALL MESSAGE
GET ALL CHARACTER with creatorID == userId

GET ALL GUILDS for user
GET ALL CHARACTER for user
Get ALL message with guilds OR character OR creatorID == userId --> GROUP BY room = type region realm name creatorID

Message Structure
    type
    region
    realm
    name
    creatorId
    id
    text

